title: Rsc Crispy Wraps
summary: Rsc Crispy Wraps requires approximately 1 hour and 15 minutes from start to finish. This recipe serves 1 and costs $5.78 per serving. One serving contains 1821 calories, 90g of protein, and 118g of fat. 1 person has made this recipe and would make it again. It works well as a pricey main course. If you have pineapple juice, cornstarch, salt, and a few other ingredients on hand, you can make it. To use up the salt you could follow this main course with the Apple Turnovers Recipe as a dessert. It is a good option if you're following a dairy free diet. With a spoonacular score of 79%, this dish is solid. Similar recipes include Crispy Chicken Wraps, Crispy Thai Chicken Wraps, and Crispy Fajita Chicken Wraps.
